OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FFurther heavy showers likely on
OL,7,FThursday and Friday, which also carry
OL,8,Fa risk of thunder. Some sunny spells
OL,9,Fin the mix too. Drier and brighter on
OL,10,FSaturday.
